title: The Day She Disappeared
description: In this Dateline classic, a missing persons case quickly becomes a homicide investigation. Police have no suspects, but a grieving family has suspicions. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on August 19, 2011.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
